    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“陛下，我们的城堡已被夷为废墟，残兵正四散逃生……”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔怔军的蒸汽巨兽与秘魔火焰席卷了帝国的每一寸土地，昔日辉煌只剩灰烬。身为流亡的国王，躲避魔怔军的围剿，带领残兵在废墟中重建经济、科技与军队，在绝境中对抗魔怔军的追击。每一次决策都关乎帝国的存亡，智慧与战略将决定帝国能否浴火重生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/5ce74e59bbd18326aaf5a2e9d5e062df.avif?t=1769997681\" alt=\"\"width=1106 height=234 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存、扩张、发展与征服：多样化战役模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >残兵散落在各地，你必须指挥他们在魔怔军的围剿下生存并守护最后据点。随着势力壮大，任务也会不断变化：护送秘魔师与工匠、拦截敌方补给、占领战略要地或资源点、进攻敌军基地，最终将魔怔军赶出大陆。每场战役都考验你的战略与决策，让你在绝境中重建帝国辉煌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/9456676d5d8633e9d6bb3dd817316e02.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" aria-label=\"各种游戏模式演示\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/9456676d5d8633e9d6bb3dd817316e02.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/9456676d5d8633e9d6bb3dd817316e02.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简化建造系统：点击即放，所见即所得</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在荒野之上，城市等待你的重建。选择建筑，点击放置即可立即建造并生效。虽然工人、建筑师和搬运工仍在运作，但繁琐微观管理已被简化，每一次布局都直接影响资源与军队运作。专注战略与发展，把分散力量整合成帝国支柱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/98df49333a2281cbdd58a05bd2411d11.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" aria-label=\"放置建筑演示\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/98df49333a2281cbdd58a05bd2411d11.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/98df49333a2281cbdd58a05bd2411d11.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >零微操单位：随意部署，自动战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >士兵、蒸汽机械与秘魔单位可以随意部署到战场，他们会自动投入战斗。无需微操任何士兵，你只需关注整体阵型与战略布局，看着军队在战场上碰撞、厮杀、互相配合，体验指挥帝国军队的宏大战争快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/a8fd35a567cf40e9928930ffad4d179e.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" aria-label=\"放置单位演示\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/a8fd35a567cf40e9928930ffad4d179e.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/a8fd35a567cf40e9928930ffad4d179e.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >秘魔与蒸汽科技：打造独特建筑与单位</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/99f1e2ad16cb558f2dfb7cf7c0819bd1.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" aria-label=\"科技树展示\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/99f1e2ad16cb558f2dfb7cf7c0819bd1.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/99f1e2ad16cb558f2dfb7cf7c0819bd1.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帝国残兵在荒野中重整旗鼓，各种蒸汽机械与秘魔科技等待你的掌控。研究蒸汽机械、禁忌秘魔或两者融合的科技，解锁特色建筑：从高效资源工坊到辅助秘魔装置，再到威力强大的防御塔与战略设施。每座建筑都直接影响资源流转与战局策略，助你重建坚实的帝国基础。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/bf08c0d588596cd42339a414d13e742a.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" aria-label=\"建筑展示\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/bf08c0d588596cd42339a414d13e742a.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/bf08c0d588596cd42339a414d13e742a.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过科技研究，你可以解锁特色单位：从坚固的蒸汽战斗机械到毁灭性的秘魔兵团，甚至融合蒸汽与秘魔的强力飞艇。每类单位拥有独特能力与战术定位，让你自由部署军队，灵活应对魔怔军进攻，打造多样化战略组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/e0c752c9e8fd272e0ae71caa8d3f8805.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" aria-label=\"单位展示\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/e0c752c9e8fd272e0ae71caa8d3f8805.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/e0c752c9e8fd272e0ae71caa8d3f8805.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战场抉择：塑造单局战略走向</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战役推进过程中，当帝国稳住局势或取得阶段性成果时，你将获得一次战略抉择。不同选择将侧重于经济、科技或军事方向，并在当前战役中持续生效。这些抉择将深刻影响帝国的发展节奏与战场表现，使每一局战役都拥有独特的战略走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/4e235480997fc2e3e5b7bd17edd77229.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/4e235480997fc2e3e5b7bd17edd77229.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/4e235480997fc2e3e5b7bd17edd77229.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由创造与分享：地图编辑器与创意工坊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置强大地图编辑器，让你在荒野、废墟与战略据点自由布置地形、建筑和单位。设计防御战、残兵求生或宏大征服战场皆可随心而为，并通过创意工坊分享或下载地图，让帝国的战争与冒险永不止步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/88809f008f0396a07c3109527a6f9315.poster.avif?t=1769997681\" aria-label=\"地图编辑器演示\" width=1170 height=810 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/88809f008f0396a07c3109527a6f9315.webm?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317570/extras/88809f008f0396a07c3109527a6f9315.mp4?t=1769997681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
